               <lb n="c56-0073__main__2"/>On</seg>my <seg xml:id="C13_app6-fMS">return</seg>I found the following letter <lb n="c56-0073__main__3"/>from my <seg xml:id="C13_app8-fMS">father. <lb n="c56-0073__main__4"/> To V.–Frankenstein <lb n="c56-0073__main__5"/>Geneva – June 2<shi ana="start" rend="sup"/> d<shi ana="end"/>– 17— <lb n="c56-0073__main__6"/>My</seg>dear <seg xml:id="C13_app12-fMS">Victor</seg>
