               </sga-add>
            </mod>your <seg xml:id="C13_app34-fMS">
               <lb n="c56-0073__main__13"/>surprise <del ana="start" rend="strikethrough" xml:id="c56-0073__main__d5e15395"/>be<del ana="end"/> ,</seg>my <seg xml:id="C13_app36-fMS">son <del ana="start" rend="strikethrough" xml:id="c56-0073__main__d5e15398"/>e<del ana="end"/> ,</seg>when <seg xml:id="C13_app38-fMS">your</seg>
            <w ana="start"/>ex<lb n="c56-0073__main__14"/>pected<w ana="end"/> a happy and <seg xml:id="C13_app40-fMS">gay</seg>
            <seg xml:id="C13_app41-fMS">welcome</seg>to <seg xml:id="C13_app43-fMS">
               <del ana="start" rend="strikethrough" xml:id="c56-0073__main__d5e15408"/>heho<del ana="end"/>
               <lb n="c56-0073__main__15"/>beh <mod xml:id="c56-0073__main__d5e15413">
                  <mdel ana="start"/>o<mdel ana="end"/>
                  <sga-add place="intralinear" xml:id="c56-0073__main__d5e15417">e </sga-add>
               </mod> ld</seg>on the <seg xml:id="C13_app45-fMS">contrary</seg>tears and <seg xml:id="C13_app47-fMS">
               <w ana="start"/>wretched<lb n="c56-0073__main__16"/>ness<w ana="end"/>.</seg>And how, Victor, can I relate our <seg xml:id="C13_app49-fMS">
               <lb n="c56-0073__main__17"/>misfortune <mod xml:id="c56-0073__main__d5e15430">
                  <mdel/>
                  <sga-add place="intralinear" xml:id="c56-0073__main__d5e15437">? </sga-add>
               </mod>
            </seg>absence cannot have rendered <lb n="c56-0073__main__18"/>you callous to our joys and <seg xml:id="C13_app51-fMS">griefs</seg>and how <seg xml:id="C13_app53-fMS">
               <lb n="c56-0073__main__19"/>can</seg>I inflict pain on <seg xml:id="C13_app55-fMS">an</seg>absent <seg xml:id="C13_app57-fMS">child.?</seg>
            <lb n="c56-0073__main__20"/>I wish to prepare you for the <seg xml:id="C13_app59-fMS">woeful</seg>
            <seg xml:id="C13_app60-fMS">
               <lb n="c56-0073__main__21"/>news</seg>but I know it is impossible; even <lb n="c56-0073__main__22"/>now your eye skims over the <seg xml:id="C13_app62-fMS">page</seg>to <lb n="c56-0073__main__23"/>seek the words which are to convey to <lb n="c56-0073__main__24"/>you the horrible tidings. <milestone unit="tei:p-END"/>
            <milestone unit="tei:p-START"/>
            <seg xml:id="C13_app64-fMS">
               <lb n="c56-0073__main__25"/>William</seg>is <seg xml:id="C13_app66-fMS">dead! That</seg>sweet <seg xml:id="C13_app68-fMS">child</seg>
            <lb n="c56-0073__main__26"/>whose smiles delighted &amp; warmed <seg xml:id="C13_app70-fMS">me</seg>
            <lb n="c56-0073__main__27"/>who was so <seg xml:id="C13_app72-fMS">gentle</seg>yet so <seg xml:id="C13_app74-fMS">gay,</seg>Victor, he <lb n="c56-0073__main__28"/>is Murdered! <milestone unit="tei:p-END"/>
            <milestone unit="tei:p-START"/>
            <seg xml:id="C13_app76-fMS">
               <lb n="c56-0073__main__29"/>I</seg>will not attempt to <seg xml:id="C13_app78-fMS">
               <del ana="start" rend="strikethrough" xml:id="c56-0073__main__d5e15471"/>o<del ana="end"/> console</seg>
            <seg xml:id="C13_app79-fMS">you</seg>
            <lb n="c56-0073__main__30"/>but will simply relate the circumstances <lb n="c56-0073__main__31"/>of the transaction. <milestone unit="tei:p-END"/>
            <milestone unit="tei:p-START"/>
            <seg xml:id="C13_app81-fMS">
               <lb n="c56-0074__main__1"/>Last thurday (May <del ana="start" rend="strikethrough" xml:id="c56-0074__main__d5e15491"/>26<del ana="end"/> 28<shi ana="start" rend="underline"/>th<shi ana="end"/>) I; <mod xml:id="c56-0074__main__d5e15497">
                  <del ana="start" rend="strikethrough" xml:id="c56-0074__main__d5e15499"/>your <sga-add place="superlinear" xml:id="c56-0074__main__d5e15501">my </sga-add>
                  <del ana="end"/>
               </mod>
               <del ana="start" rend="strikethrough" xml:id="c56-0074__main__d5e15507"/>cousin<del ana="end"/>
            </seg>
            <lb n="c56-0074__main__2"/>my <seg xml:id="C13_app85-fMS">niece</seg>and your two <seg xml:id="C13_app87-fMS">brothers</seg>went to <lb n="c56-0074__main__3"/>walk in Plainpalais. The evening was <lb n="c56-0074__main__4"/>warm and serene, and we prolonged our <lb n="c56-0074__main__5"/>walk <seg xml:id="C13_app89-fMS">
               <del ana="start" rend="strikethrough" xml:id="c56-0074__main__d5e15518"/>fat<del ana="end"/> farther than usual. It was</seg>
            <seg xml:id="C13_app90-fMS">
               <lb n="c56-0074__main__6"/>
               <del ana="start" rend="strikethrough" xml:id="c56-0074__main__d5e15524"/>
               <shi ana="start" rend="underline"/>ale<shi ana="end"/>
               <del ana="end"/> already dusk before we thought of</seg>
            <seg part="I" xml:id="C13_app91-fMS__I">
               <lb n="c56-0074__main__7"/>returning </seg>
            <mod xml:id="c56-0074__main__d5e15532">
